        <h1>Standard Deduction 2026: Projected Amounts and What to Expect</h1>
        <p class="qa-meta">Updated May 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Projected estimates only &nbsp;|&nbsp; Official IRS amounts expected October 2026</p>
        <p>The IRS has not yet announced the official 2026 standard deduction. Based on current inflation data and the C-CPI-U adjustment method, the projected amount is approximately $15,500 for single filers and $31,000 for married filing jointly. This page will be updated when the IRS releases official figures.</p>
        <div class="year-nav">
          <a href="/standard-deduction-2025">2025 Amounts (Official)</a>
